content:
- Jesus Burgess, Augur, Doc Q, and Stronger have acquired Devil Fruit powers. Burgess has the Riki Riki no Mi, Auger has the Wapu Wapu no Mi, Doc Q has the Shiku Shiku no Mi, Stronger has the Uma Uma no Mi, Model: Pegasus, Avalo Pizarro has the Shima Shima no Mi, and Vasco Shot has the Gabu Gabu no Mi. As a result, Blackbeard confirms that all of his officers now have Devil Fruit powers, thus completing his quest of hunting down powerful Devil Fruits.
			- In addition, the name of Sanjuan Wolf's previously unnamed Devil Fruit is revealed to be the Deka Deka no Mi.
